name: Hutt Bounty
Lore: '''Chissaa, picha gawanki Chewbacca. Yupon cogorato kama walpa kyess kashung kawa Wookiee.''',
Text: 'Deploy on an opponent''s smuggler, gambler, or thief. If subsequently captured by a bounty hunter and then transfered to Jabba''s Palace Dungeon, retrieve Force equal to character''s forfeit (+6 if Han) and lose effect. (Immune to Alter.)',
